platform, apparently the controls for this lift.  Each thick chain has a
painted wooden handle attached to its bottom link in order to provide a
steady grip for operation.  One of the ragged wooden handles is red, its
paint heavily worn off and faded.  The other handle has been colored
blue, its chipped surface flaking off with every pull.
